Report on Chat Sessions

Gain insight into your agentsâ€™ chat activities by building reports about Chat sessions.

Available in: Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience.
Available in: Performance Editions, Essentials, Unlimited, and Enterprise Editions with Service Cloud or Sales Cloud.

To create, edit, and delete reports:
Create and Customize Reports
AND
Report Builder

IMPORTANT The legacy chat product is scheduled for retirement on February 14, 2026. Create a custom report type using Chat Sessions as the primary object.
Create a new Chat report using the Report Builder in Salesforce Classic or the Reports tab in Lightning Experience.
Customize your report to include the columns of information you want to feature.
Save or run the report.
title: Report on Chat Sessions in Service Cloud
